om":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":163,"column":3,"offset":15231},"end":{"line":163,"column":28,"offset":15256},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171823"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421171457","id":"zettel.20260421171457","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":97,"column":3,"offset":7844},"end":{"line":97,"column":28,"offset":7869},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171823"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.bmad-analysis-phase","id":"zettel.literature.bmad-analysis-phase","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":3,"offset":1346},"end":{"line":31,"column":28,"offset":1371},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171823"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.ai-native","id":"zettel.moc.ai-native","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":3,"offset":3468},"end":{"line":43,"column":28,"offset":3493},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171823"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":3,"offset":4307},"end":{"line":57,"column":28,"offset":4332},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171823"}],"anchors":{"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka":{"type":"header","text":"Pertanyaan yang dibuka","value":"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"klaim-utama":{"type":"header","text":"Klaim utama","value":"klaim-utama","line":21,"column":0,"depth":2},"fungsi-epistemic-filter":{"type":"header","text":"Fungsi epistemic filter","value":"fungsi-epistemic-filter","line":27,"column":0,"depth":2},"implikasi-untuk-prd-dan-architecture":{"type":"header","text":"Implikasi untuk PRD dan architecture","value":"implikasi-untuk-prd-dan-architecture","line":38,"column":0,"depth":2},"lihat-juga":{"type":"header","text":"Lihat juga","value":"lihat-juga","line":44,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"bmad-analysis-phase-sebagai-epistemic-filter-sebelum-prd\">BMAD analysis phase sebagai epistemic filter sebelum PRD<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bmad-analysis-phase-sebagai-epistemic-filter-sebelum-prd\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\">Pertanyaan yang dibuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Kenapa BMAD menempatkan analysis sebagai filter epistemik?</li>\n<li>Apa beda hasil sebelum dan sesudah filter ini?</li>\n<li>Bagaimana phase ini melindungi PRD dan architecture?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"klaim-utama\">Klaim utama<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#klaim-utama\"></a></h2>\n<p>BMAD analysis phase bukan sekadar fase riset tambahan. Ia adalah momen untuk menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum membentuk struktur formal.</p>\n<p>Jika ide masih kabur, PRD akan mengunci ketidakjelasan itu. Architecture akan mengambil keputusan atas dasar asumsi yang sama. Analysis phase adalah filter yang memaksa tim memeriksa dan membersihkan asumsi sebelum tahap formal dimulai.</p>\n<h2 id=\"fungsi-epistemic-filter\">Fungsi epistemic filter<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#fungsi-epistemic-filter\"></a></h2>\n<p>Dalam BMAD, phase ini menempatkan kegagalan di titik paling murah. Ia hanya ingin memastikan bahwa ide yang dibawa ke planning:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>sudah akrab dengan realitas pasar,</li>\n<li>sudah memiliki konteks domain,</li>\n<li>sudah melewati pemeriksaan kelayakan teknis,</li>\n<li>tidak hanya muncul sebagai perasaan dalam kepala.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Tanpa filter ini, planning berubah menjadi proses menyusun ulang ketidakjelasan. Dengan filter ini, planning menjadi proses merapikan insight.</p>\n<h2 id=\"implikasi-untuk-prd-dan-architecture\">Implikasi untuk PRD dan architecture<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#implikasi-untuk-prd-dan-architecture\"></a></h2>\n<p>Analisis yang berhasil mengubah PRD dari dokumen yang \"mendefinisikan\" menjadi dokumen yang \"menyatakan\" hasil pemikiran yang lebih matang.</p>\n<p>Architecture pun menjadi lebih bertahan karena ia didirikan di atas asumsi yang teruji. Tanpa analysis, architecture akan terkunci pada tebakan teknis yang rawan salah.</p>\n<h2 id=\"lihat-juga\">Lihat juga<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lihat-juga\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a> — BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171638\">BMAD PRFAQ menguji ide dengan pendekatan adversarial sebelum planning</a> — BMAD PRFAQ menguji ide dengan pendekatan adversarial sebelum planning</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">bmad (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">analysis-phase (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">epistemic-filter (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-native (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.bmad-analysis-phase\">BMAD Analysis Phase sebagai literature note</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.ai-native\">MOC AI-native engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true